{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127211221162921984734521.jpeg/3nDbzXHbhDY7eemlt88jFkW9Y8JCnB9VBbIVny-yFZ8\" alt=\"今日早上葉先生手持鮮花返回宏泰閣。（黃偉民攝）\"><figcaption>今日早上葉先生手持鮮花返回宏泰閣。（黃偉民攝）</figcaption></figure><p>早上9時，葉先生手持花束偕兒子到來，但眾人行色匆匆，他只表示希望上樓取回物件便急步前行。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127210732522311680402389.jpeg/bv4epju9gmKPnmD5saGdLvcHE9wu3VN3vE9TIZZPUyE\" alt=\"今日早上葉先生帶同鮮花回到宏福苑。（黃偉民攝）\"><figcaption>今日早上葉先生帶同鮮花回到宏福苑。（黃偉民攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-02T04:44:22.159125+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":92,"images":2,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}